flowRoot.flowPara: Whether serving few or many, openSUSE offers what Administrators need. Set up a mail, web or file server, initiate a VM or Firewall in a few clicks. System tool YaST brings both control and ease of use.
openSUSE ships the 4 major desktops as equals. We aim to empower, not limit you! With the quality and polish of our products we fit even the most demanding needs.

Join the ranks of those using openSUSE for their development. Unparalelled stability and all the needed tools combined with the power of OBS for both retrieving and distributing the latest packages are what openSUSE brings to you. Projects like KDE, GNOME3 and Scribus are build on openSUSE primairily - because we have what it takes!

openSUSE believes in Freedom and creating to the benefit of all! Which is why we initiate cross-distribution and cross-desktop projects like Appstream and release our technologies like OBS as Free Software.
openSUSE is a free Linux-based operating system for your PC. You can surf the web, manage your e-mails and photos, do office work, play videos or music
An openSUSE DVD includes everything you need to get your desktop, laptop, or server up and running with Linux in no time!
